Automatic.Title: Automatic Questions
Automatic.AutomaticPageDescription: This page allows the AO/CM to view all the listed Automatic questions with details like Question Title, Question Type and Question description along with Options. It displays “Response Analysis” with Correct/incorrect answers. Each question can be moderated on click of respective “Moderate” button.
Automatic.ModeratePageDescription: This page allows the AO/CM to Moderate the Automatic question. It displays question details and “Response Analysis” with Correct/incorrect answers. Remarks should be provided before moderating.
Automatic.Moderatealertmessage: Are you sure, you want to Moderate the score ?
Automatic.Moderatealertmessage1: Are you sure, you want to Re-Moderate the score ?
Automatic.note: The Question can be seen after the closure of the Examination.
